#### 2.2 Data Requirements Discovery

Identify core entities and relationships:

```
Question: "What are the main data entities this system will manage?"
Options:
  - "Users/Accounts"
  - "Products/Inventory"
  - "Orders/Transactions"
  - "Content/Documents"
  - "Events/Activities"
multiSelect: true
```

